    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. The S54 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies, with the VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, positive engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings that maintain factory-spec suspension geometry. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no evidence of swirl marks or oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A mechanically synchronized, turnkey specimen for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
