    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, preserved by a full-front Paint Protection Film (PPF) and a multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like gloss. There are absolutely no chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. The interior is equally pristine; the Black Dakota leather seats show no signs of wear, the carbon fiber trim is scratch-free, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this M2 is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized BMW centers. It has never been tracked, modified, or driven in inclement weather. The wheels are entirely free of curb rash and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires. This is an exceptional opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a perfect example of one of BMW's finest driver's cars. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a thick binder of service documentation.",
